First at all thank you so much for this amazing library!

I was trying to upgrade my virtualenv with the last version in windows and I received an error about encoding. 

Cloning the repository and changing in the setup.py:
def readme():
    with open('README.rst') as f:
        return f.read()

For this, solved my problem the next change:
def readme():
    with open('README.rst', encoding='utf-8') as f:
        return f.read()

If somebody has the same problem, maybe this could help you to solve it.
Best regards and thank you for your work @eternnoir!!

